headline: AI-Related Stocks Sink Lower
summary: Tech stocks are getting a beating, with the Nasdaq now comfortably down more than a full percentage and ready to end this week with a loss. Digging deeper, some of the pain is stemming from stocks like Astera Labs, a company dabbling in AI Infrastructure.
